msgid ""
"If you are outside the US, we recommend NOWPayments (lowest fees, direct to "
"your wallet). If you are in the US, Stripe Crypto is also an option. You can"
" enable multiple services and let your visitors choose!"
msgstr ""
"Če ste izven ZDA, priporočamo NOWPayments (najnižje pristojbine, neposredno "
"na vaš denarnik). Če ste v ZDA, je Stripe Crypto tudi možnost. Omogočite več"
" storitev in pustite, da si vaši obiskovalci izberejo!"

